data.description: Welcome to this beautiful colonial style home in Spring Grove School District.  Bright and open floor plan, many upgrades throughout.  Located minutes from Little Creek Golf Course and Lake Pahagaco, where you can enjoy fishing , boating and golfing.  Newer roof and Pergo luxury vinyl plank flooring, which is easy to care for.  Tray ceilings, crown molding and high ceilings throughout.  Spacious kitchen with large island, Corian countertops, lots of cabinets and stainless steel appliances.  Family room boasts a floor to ceiling stone fireplace, perfect for chilly nights.  Separate dining room with a large bay window.  Additional formal living room with glass doors perfect for a work space or quiet reading area.  Primary suite has its own mini-split A/C, vaulted ceilings, private bath with walk-in shower and soaking tub.  Three other spacious bedrooms all with lots of closet space.  First floor laundry. Large deck & covered front porch.  Unfinished lower level waits for your touches.  Has egress window and is plumbed for future bath.  Take a tour and call this home.
